    "intro": "Interpretation asks what the text means — moving from observation to the author's intent in his original context and its place in the canon's argument. The movements below trace Psalm 3's argument from the historical crisis through the confessional pivot to the doxological conclusion. Where Hebrew lexical detail sharpens the English, a brief note supplements the exposition.",
